                     <interp inst="def2-525-18700606" type="given" value="JOSEPH ALFRED"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">JOSEPH ALFRED BERGER</hi> (20)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18700606-525-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18700606-525-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18700606-525-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>, Unlawfully uttering a medal resembling a shilling, to <persName id="t18700606-name-375" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18700606-name-375" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18700606-name-375" type="surname" value="CLARKE"></interp>
